logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 > %2 THEN  TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , %1, %3) ELSE  TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , %1, %2) END
CASE  WHEN  ABS( TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY ,  IFNULL(%1, %2), %3)) <=  VALUEOF(%4) THEN 1.0d ELSE 0.0d END
CASE  WHEN  ABS(%1) <=  VALUEOF(%2) THEN 1.0d ELSE 0.0d END
CASE  WHEN  ABS( TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , %1, %2)) <= 2 THEN 1.0d ELSE 0.0d END
CASE  WHEN  ABS(%1) <= 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
CAST ( TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_HOUR , %1,  IFNULL(%2,  CURRENT_DATE )) AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) / 24
